<dl id="n54106h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n54" href="#n54106h">N54 (VI.B.45)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n54all.htm#n54106h"> 106(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> M. Hashimite</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[T]</font>he greater number of the descendants of Hashim, Mohammed&apos;s great grandfather, stood by their kinsman. But the <mark>Hashimites</mark>, as they were called, could not hope to hold their own againt the rest of the tribe of Kuraysh. <small> Edith Holland, <a name="EHSM" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#EHSM"><cite title="source">The Story of Mohammed</cite></a> (1914) 58</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
